    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made this soup last weekend and it was great!  I too added a bit more stock (not home made but still wonderful).  I don&#8217;t know how it would feed four though. :O  We had enough for two small bowls as it is VERY rich but as a treat, well it was just that.  Thank you for inspiring us!</p>
