    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh sorry, I forgot to add one thing!  I lived in Paris for years and am now an expat in another foreign city &#8211; Hong Kong.  Its been unseasonably &#8220;cold&#8221; here, so I was nostalgically craving Parisian food (don&#8217;t ask)!  Anyway, this this beautiful soup really made my day.  Thank you!</p>
